Package fr.warzou.virtualcard.utils.property

Interface PropertyMap

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractLockablePropertyMap, AbstractModuleFile.ImplPropertyMap, AbstractPropertyMap, Captor.CaptorPropertyMap, CardClock.ClockPropertyMap, Container.ContainerPropertyMap, Conveyor.ConveyorPropertyMap, Dropper.DropperPropertyMap, JsonModule.LockablePropertyMap, ModuleManager.ImplPropertyMap, PacketParser.LockablePropertyMap, PluginRegister.LockablePropertyMap, Pusher.PusherPropertyMap
public interface PropertyMap
This interface allows the links between String in key, and a generic object in value.

This interface is quickly like a Map in the principe.

However key need to be a String and the value in generic.

Version:
0.0.2
Author:
Warzou
